{
  "stem": "8527.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I have a problem with my religion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not comfortable in the synagogue, because I forgot how to pray in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now I have to look on the other side of the page to pray.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had a problem with God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why would God allow this to happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if he did allow it to happen as a punishment to his people, why the children?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have trouble with that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Have you come to any kind of resolution about that?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I'll ever totally resolve it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm becoming more at peace with myself than I used to be, but it never goes away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've talked to different people, questioning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't like dogma.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really despise dogma.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I despise right wings, whether it's my religion or anybody else's religion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I strongly believe that in the name of God and the name of religion, the greatest atrocities are being committed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I have a problem with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I made some mistakes with my children, because when they were growing up I didn't want to put any baggage on their shoulders with my background.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I overcompensated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wanted them to be their own people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In fact, I didn't-- my children didn't have bar mitzvahs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In my own mind, I felt that they should be able to make their own decisions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Which I realize now that was wrong, because I gave them too much freedom at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But what comes around what-- goes around comes around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My son is now going to Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He's 38 years old.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He wants to become bar mitzvah, and I'm the proudest person I could possibly be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, I go to Hebrew school with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I figure if it's good enough for him, it's good enough for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
